value:
They ventured deep into the forest.
The sky grew dark and foreboding...

Did something move in the bushes?!
Their reflexes kicked in and they hid!

An enemy? Oh, it was just a frog!
They both heaved a sigh of relief.

Fireflies gently flittered around them.
What an ethereal, soothing sight!

$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,
and then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest
value applied. Does not stack.)
